Qatar to Build First World Cup Soccer Stadium by 2015, QNA Says

-- B y   R o b e r t   T u t t l e
-- 
2011-06-06T11:30:28Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-06/qatar-to-build-first-world-cup-soccer-stadium-by-2015-qna-says.html
Qatar plans to complete construction
of the first stadium for the 2022  World Cup  of soccer by 2015,
the state-run Qatar News Agency said, citing Qatar 2022 Supreme
Committee Secretary General Hassan Al Thawadi.  “Program management” for the stadium project will be
assigned by the end of this year, QNA said. Prior to the World
Cup, Qatar plans to host a major soccer tournament in 2020 and
the Confederation Cup in 2021, the news agency said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
 Robert Tuttle  in Doha at 
 rtuttle@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Stephen Voss on   sev@bloomberg.net  